From: oscar.perpinan en upm.es (Oscar =?UTF-8?B?UGVycGnDsWFu?= Lamigueiro)
Date: Wed, 13 Jul 2011 16:51:23 +0200
Subject: [R-es] Extraer datos mensuales de una serie temporal
In-Reply-To: <5763A52F-B75C-4956-B169-9808C58922DA@iberstat.es>
References: <4E1D76FB.8090204@ceam.es>
